<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="iddd2ccc2e-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section is comprised of <ref href="/us/pl/116/260/dI/s115">section 115 of div. I of Pub. L. 116–260</ref>. Subsec. (d) of section 115 amended <ref href="/us/usc/t2/s5507">section 5507 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
